<li>&quot;Stop using so damn many ellipses!&quot;</li>
<li>&quot;Would it kill you to spell check?&quot;</li>
<li>&quot;Grammar is not optional&quot;</li>
<li>&quot;Read it back before your hit 'Post it' &quot;</li>
</ol>
<p>I'm sure there are other things that can be added to the &quot;How To&quot; pages&#8230;</p>

